{"tid":310262,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解一個人可以咁痴情","createTime":"2017-07-05T16:01:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T15:31:06.000Z","uid":126876,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6e424874254913ed4b011948f2b62e054992f9c2","tid":310262,"uid":126876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:01:28.000Z","msg":"我由小學四年班暗戀一個細一年嘅男仔到家陣U grad。 <br />\n高中之前佢當我普通朋友咁相處,但有時佢啲行為例如摸頭落雨主動遮我等等,搞到我好亂又驚自作多情(自己知自己事,樣衰又有啲肥妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ),就一直冇表白到。高中後疏遠咗,我依然痴漢地碌佢fb ig睇住佢開始拍拖換囡囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。 再後啲發現佢入咗同我同一間U, 起campus見到佢都只敢遠觀。<br />\n<br />\n求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好似中咗毒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點先可以走出佢個陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9bfa16dadf41b97f1432cd510893c7c4ced2c77","tid":310262,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:04:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Fat Fat"},{"pid":"c88895236d7a15dc0f764a977e9352252fe7dda1","tid":310262,"uid":6869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:15:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"708380eeb2e46133d76d15732b481cc2b5ae49ae","tid":310262,"uid":126876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:33:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c465df5e10672934c51415720cca7334c84365","tid":310262,"uid":112666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T16:36:42.000Z","msg":"有冇拍過拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b193ba999ab5e1f32eeda234365ee012035bf4c7","tid":310262,"uid":1274,"like":0,"dislike":